title: Cubase LE winxp/win2k (Supports ReWire!)
description:
Cubase LE v1.x for Windows XP / 2000 (REWIRE CAPABLE)

This version requires no dongle or crack. 
It was originally bundled with an EMU audio interface that i bought (the EMU0404USB).
This version will support Rewire connectivity to ReWire capable Hosts & Slaves
such as: 

Propellerheads Reason
Propellerheds Rebirth
Ableton Live
Arturia Storm
Cakewalk Sonar
Celemony Melodyne
Cockos Reaper
Digidesign Pro Tools
Emagic Logic 5.5
ImageLine FL Studio & Fruity Loops
Magix Samplitude
Presonus Studio One
Sony Acid Pro
Steinberg Nuendo

Features:
simultaneous playback 48 tracks
midi tracks 64
inserts 2
group channels 4
fx return no
vst instrument slot 2
midi inserts no
rewire 2 support yes
undo steps 10
vst audio effects included 21
vst instruments included 3

For full complete information on the limitations of this free ReWire capable Cubase Version
visit or download the following pdf document: ftp://ftp.steinberg.net/Download/Cubase_SX_3/Docs_English/All_Cubase_Feature_Comparison.pdf
